Class NameRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.gnsapp.recordmap.NameRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.Summarizable, Comparable<NameRecord>

    public class NameRecord
extends Object
implements Comparable<NameRecord>, edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.Summarizable
    The name record. It specifies what is store in the database for system and user fields. This is also the in memory version of what is store in the database. Probably could just be a JSON Object.

    abhigyan
